title: Businessweek Talks- Dell Chair and CEO Michael Dell
itunes:title: Businessweek Talks- Dell Chair and CEO Michael Dell
description:
Michael Dell, Founder, Chairman and CEO of Dell Technologies, discusses his memoir "Play Nice But Win: A CEO’s Journey From Founder to Leader." Dell speaks with Bloomberg Businessweek anchors Carol Massar and Tim Stenovec in the latest edition of Businessweek Talks.
